body:
With this PR you can really skip the weak labeling process of the supervision tutorial (single-label) by downloading the training/test data from the HF Hub, before it was not really possible. It also fixes the results, they were a bit off.

A small cosmetical fix is also done for the find label error tutorial.

@frascuchon it also clarifies which lines exactly you have to substitute when loading the data from the Hub

This PR updates the "Define rules" references in our docs, and adds a video to the weak supervision multi-label tutorial.

It also updates the tooltips in the UI to be more accurate in the case of multi-label tasks.
@leiyre could you have a quick look at the tooltip changes, hope i did not mess up.
